  Forge Blocks 🚀

  A block-based page editor with inline markdown, code, links, regrets, and ✨
  emoji. Focus a block to edit its raw source; press / on an empty block for the
  block palette.

  Typography

  • Bullet lists with bold entries

    • nested by indent

